text: Kurdzhipskaya () is a rural locality (a stanitsa) in Krasnooktyabrskoye Rural Settlement of Maykopsky District, Russia. The population was 1618 as of 2018. There are 18 streets. == Geography == The stanitsa is located 16 km south of Maykop. == References == Category:Rural localities in Maykopsky District
title: Kurdzhipskaya
